Package: tidycharts
Type: Package
Title: Create interactive charts using the tidy syntax you know and love!
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Vedha Viyash
Maintainer: Vedha Viyash <vedhaviyash4@gmail.com>
Description: The objective of this package is to allow you to create interactive charts
    using syntax similar to the grammar of graphics so you can spend less time figuring out
    how to plot and more time visualizing the data.
    This package provides a easy to use interface to create plots using 'plotly'.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5),
    plotly
Imports:
    rlang,
    stats,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    magrittr,
    colorspace
Suggests:
    testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2.9000
